<% content_for :title do %>
    Build a Great New Product!
<% end %>

<div id="typed-strings">
  <p>You can... learn to code</p>
  <p>You can... build your own product</p>
  <p>You can... launch a new career!</p>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid svg-background" style="background-image: url('/confetti-doodles.svg');">
  <div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row d-flex align-items-center">
      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="display-4">Build Something Great</h1>
        <h3>
          <span id="typed"></span>
        </h3>
      </div>

      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-4">

        <div class="card p-3">

          <div class="font-weight-bold text-center f-md">Get Started For Free</div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <%= link_to user_google_oauth2_omniauth_authorize_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block my-3' do %>
                <i class="fab fa-google"></i> &nbsp;&nbsp; Sign up with Google
            <% end %>
          </div>

          <h5 class="text-center">or</h5>

          <%= render 'shared/signup_form' %>

        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid section my-5 py-5">
  <div class="container">

    <h2 class="text-center">What is an MVP?</h2>


    <div class="row">

      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-8 offset-md-2">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="card-text f-md">
              Good Question.
            </p>

            <p class="card-text f-md">
              It is a Minimum Viable Product.  So... it must be viable and it must be a product, but created
              with the minimum amount of effort.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>


    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid light-background">
  <div class="container pt-5">

    <div class="row">

      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 mb-5 section d-flex align-items-center">

        <h2 class="text-center">What makes MVP Starter different?</h2>

      </div>

      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 mb-5">

        <div class="card h-100">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title text-center text-primary"><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> Understanding</h5>
            <p class="card-text f-md">
              Once you <strong>fully understand</strong> an idea it becomes yours and no one can take it away from you.
              Our goal is to help you understand and we will continue to distill large ideas and frameworks it easily
              digestible bits.
            </p>

            <p class="card-text f-md">
              Our goal is to <strong>help you understand</strong> and we will continue to distill complex ideas into
              easily digestible bits.
            </p>

            <p class="card-text f-md">
              We are able to achieve this because of hard won knowledge built up over decades. So we can
              see what is important and help you navigate the learning landscape in a much shorter time.
            </p>

          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid section">
  <div class="container pt-5">

    <h2 class="text-center mb-3">Your Instructor</h2>

    <div class="row">

      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-8 mb-5">

        <div class="card h-100">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title text-center text-primary"><i class="fas fa-user-graduate"></i>
              <strong>Harris Reynolds</strong></h5>

            <p class="card-text f-md">
              I have two great passions professionally: <strong>learning</strong> and <strong>teaching</strong>.
            </p>

            <p class="card-text f-md">
              I've always been curious and enjoyed learning. This is great because this is one of the most important
              characteristics you need to be successful building software.
            </p>

            <p class="card-text f-md">
              And I've also always enjoyed teaching. I've built MVP Starter completely in the public in videos in order to
              share my knowledge with the world. Our first course is just the beginning.
            </p>

          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-4 mb-5 d-flex align-items-center">

        <img class="rounded-circle w-100" src="/harris-face-square.png">

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<script>
    var typed = new Typed('#typed', {
        stringsElement: '#typed-strings',
        typeSpeed: 40,
        backDelay: 1200,
        backSpeed: 20,
        smartBackspace: true // Default value
    });
</script>